{"tid":1426753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以手提風炮機於香港多處掘出大坑","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:15.000Z","uid":99610,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"91672bbb87ff203aea9f57043837011eb34535f8","tid":1426753,"uid":99610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到消息，一班黑衣蒙面人，喺新填地街購入多部手提風炮機，打算向主要道路，掘出大坑，堵塞車輛，龍翔道，屯門公路，往機場來回，東區走廊，請各市民留意路面情況。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQT2qfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQT2qfW.png&h=65d1bcd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RHNCd9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRHNCd9i.png&h=0a0a8323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>深坑小心⚠⚠<br />\n九龍<br />\n*西隧出，往尖咀上橋前左線(即爆胎)<br />\n*觀塘聯合醫院出來燈口(極深)<br />\n*觀塘道往九龍灣方向創紀之城對出快線(深坑)<br />\n*半島酒店最左線轉入彌敦道<br />\n*漆咸道歐化對出向機隧方向中線<br />\n*櫻桃街奧海城巴士站對出<br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n*金鐘道左轉軍器廠街最內線<br />\n*維園興發街最左線<br />\n*香港仔隧道往香港仔方向入口左邊<br />\n*司徒拔道上山近未到廣安醫院天橋（即時爆軚）<br />\n<br />\n新界<br />\n*葵涌往九龍，美孚出口慢線(即爆胎)<br />\n*錦田公路羅屋村向林錦方向(極深)<br />\n*往石門大迴旋一出石門口，左中線<br />\n*火炭落高速公路往新城市方向<br />\n*獅隧入新界慢線沙田路城門河匯合位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n究竟邊度有得買呢啲風炮機？<br />\n咁大殺傷力嘅話我需要報警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2f5e9e3fa70a1d5b1703ce5f0f64094e3fa07d","tid":1426753,"uid":19743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"問左多啦A夢借空氣炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ac212c8ea54797edf3e8ec3607774cd5ebae8e","tid":1426753,"uid":131522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b2f5e9e3fa70a1d5b1703ce5f0f64094e3fa07d","tid":1426753,"uid":19743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"問左多啦A夢借空氣炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"穿牆圈黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225ecb4529ef1e500e6fc06f23d3db324367d846","tid":1426753,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:49:20.000Z","msg":"幫手推下呢個post<br />\n<br />\n每個星期三都係成場運動嘅轉捩點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426772</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de6261d3d1dc6674a7f2aebca3aa74f9c2e98501","tid":1426753,"uid":172227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"地鼠咩，話掘就掘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fa4028da8896a64028f4639eba7c6ef2b7debe","tid":1426753,"uid":99610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"啲長輩瘋傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb147ffbac10d31346092c987679c0ce9884ca55","tid":1426753,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"咁都信個啲真係死咗佢算，即係你屈外國勢力偷運過嚟都好，屌你老母街邊買喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2de4a487b8043c250fbe38a4f1f016c72cf67d9","tid":1426753,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"如果真係咁勁，d黑警盾牌咪仲硬過石屎？都唔用腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a4fc467154d40466e3495e17e34b4ffa721159","tid":1426753,"uid":224510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"點會掘到空心<br />\n<br />\n明顯水土流失地陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bdc9dbf07ca2b112e195fcfc74d1025ab7695a","tid":1426753